    "description": "Genus-wide Yersinia core-genome multilocus sequence typing for species identification and strain characterization.\n\nYersinia Sequence Typing Home Page.\n\nThis page provides access to genotypic data for Yersinia isolates based on Multilocus Sequence Typing (MLST) and core genome MLST (cgMLST). See references for more details.\n\nMultilocus sequence typing (MLST) databases and software.\n\nThis site uses two linked databases powered by the BIGSdb genomics platform.\n\nRecent publications using MLST in Yersinia research.\n\nPrimers used for amplification and sequencing.\n\n||| COMMON LINK WITH (PUB. & NAME DIFFERENT) bio.tools/aria (PASTEUR.FR), bio.tools/BOOSTER (PASTEUR.FR), bio.tools/Galaxy_Pasteur (PASTEUR.FR), bio.tools/PastML (PASTEUR.FR), bio.tools/checkmyindex (PASTEUR.FR).\n\n||| CORRECT NAME OF TOOL COULD ALSO BE 'Yersinia isolates'",
